{"type": "article", "id": 17707, "title": "旅行箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-18T06:40:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 125, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134831WYXHJysOmG9TP8ZC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个专为年轻人设计的旅行箱，它可以承受 200 斤以内的人坐在上面。箱子的最上面可以直接打开，放一些随身的电子产品，也可以拆下的当做盒子带到另外的地方。打开箱子后，里面有一块可移动的板，将箱子的内部空间分成上下两部分，成为一个带两个格子的柜子。有红、蓝、粉三种颜色可选，<a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/jurni-the-ultimate-sit-on-carry-on-suitcase#/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"http://cms.qdaily.com/uploads/image/201511/e7b631a1c693.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" title=\" \" alt=\" \">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144841Ij3J5w7lMu6geb0y.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"314\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144842PQOMNaYfVG9nTCZy.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66612903\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261448439hbcdNuJK2GDTieZ.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"332\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.53548387\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144844jK5RahQfvFgWTJ9c.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"197\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.31774194\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}